Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class MutableIidMap<V>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.MutableHasLongMap<InstrumentId,​V>
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.MutableIidMap<V>
public class MutableIidMap<V>
extends MutableHasLongMap<InstrumentId,​V>
Like an IidMap, but mutable.

Since we rarely pass mutable objects around, this is mostly used to build up a map and then "lock" it in place as an immutable IidMap.
